Package com.turnout.ws.exception

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomExceptionMapper
    This class used to map Java exceptions to Response.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommentsNotEmptyException
    Exception thrown when comments field are empty because comments can not store an empty value in database.
    CurrentPasswordNotMatchedException
    Exception thrown when current pass word not match with user's entered password.
    NoSufficientGainedPointsException
    Exception thrown when there is no sufficient gained point while redeeming reward.
    PartyDeviceNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when there is no such a device.
    PartyEmailValidateException
    Exception thrown when entered email id is not an usual format or when it may not be an valid email id.
    PartyExistException
    Exception thrown when entered party is already exist in database.
    PartyNameValidateException
    Exception thrown when entered party name is not valid or it may contain alpha numeric value.
    PartyNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when entered party is not found.
    RewardNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when entered reward is not found in database.
    VoucherNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when entered voucher is not found in database.
    WrongAccessTokenException
    Exception thrown when entered access token of instagram is wrong or not a valid one.
    WrongVerifyCodeException
    Exception thrown when temporary verification code does not match with user's entered code.
